{"body": "updated to lazy observe everything, simplified a lot, but a few remaining problems:\n\n - fails to observe nameless classes (a = Class.new; observe a) since they have no name\n - if we want to also observe nameless classes we need 2 lists or a list that contains nameless classes and class-names\n - people using/overwriting observed_classes are in for a surprise -> maybe switch to observed_class_names to avoid confusion + deprecation warning if the method is defined\n\n(still missing load_all!, to little time today :) )\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7240771", "created_at": "2012-07-25T05:03:01Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7064#issuecomment-7240771", "updated_at": "2012-07-25T05:03:01Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7064, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/grosser", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/59436ecd4fe6ad7c34f67654d839f05f?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc474b217c91de1f9864507a1363f795d.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/received_events", "gravatar_id": "59436ecd4fe6ad7c34f67654d839f05f", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "grosser", "type": "User", "id": 11367, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/grosser/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e0b2cbd354364b900cd89"}, "id": 7240771, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7064"}
